data.description: Welcome to Shorewood East Condo living! This modernized 1 bed, 1 bath condo offers captivating Columbia River views from your personal balcony. Water, sewer, and trash expenses are all included. Brand-new stainless-steel dishwasher. Dive into the year-round pool, hit the advanced fitness center, and relax in the welcoming community space. With added conveniences like a mail room, ADA doorways, laundry amenities, and accessible elevators, this is the condo lifestyle you've been waiting for.
